article_id:1625,category_name:News,title_name:Regarding Adjustments to the Adventurer Vice,image_path:,message:<div>As part of the balance adjustments made to dragons and adventurers in the Version 2.0.0 update, the power of the adventurer Vice&#39;s skills after unlocking his mana spiral was adjusted downward before balance adjustments were applied.</div><div><br></div><div>This action was taken upon determination that Vice&#39;s performance after unlocking his mana spiral, if left as-is, may adversely impact the game&#39;s balance and play experience even after the adjustments made in Version 2.0.0.</div><div><br></div><div>The adjustments are detailed below.</div><div><br></div><div>■Adjustments</div><div>・Decreased shadow damage dealt by Fatal Blow Lv. 4 and added an effect that inflicts poison.</div><div>・Decreased shadow damage dealt by Lethal Edge Lv. 3.</div><div><br></div><div>As a goodwill gesture for these adjustments, affected players will be sent two Champion&#39;s Testaments and all players will be sent 600 wyrmite.</div><div><br></div><div>■Affected players</div><div>Players who unlocked Vice&#39;s mana spiral before the release of Version 2.0.0</div><div><br></div><div>■Goodwill Gesture for affected players</div><div>Champion&#39;s Testament &times; 2</div><div><br></div><div>■Goodwill Gesture for all players</div><div>Wyrmite &times; 600</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for your understanding.</div>,start_time:1601002800,update_time1600933513